title: Art Institute of Chicago Rock Eraser Set
description:
Erasers developed with our current logo, designed in 2008 by Abbott Miller, partner of Pentagram.

Erase your mistakes with this colorful set of three erasers shaped like rocks. 

  • Dimensions: 1.33 x 1.57 x 1.06 in. each
  • Set of three.
  • Material: Rubber.
  • Colors: Green, Blue, Purple, Pink.
